@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Last updated: October 2024</p>

    <h4>1. Introduction</h4>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.</p>

    <h4>2. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal details (name, email, etc.) for account creation and order tracking.</li>
        <li>Usage data to improve app functionality and user experience.</li>
        <li>Payment information for completing transactions securely.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. How We Use Your Data</h4>
    <p>We use your personal information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and improve our services.</li>
        <li>Process orders and deliver products.</li>
        <li>Send notifications about orders, special offers, or updates.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>4. Sharing Your Information</h4>
    <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties, except where necessary to process orders or comply with the law.</p>

    <h4>5. Data Security</h4>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to ensure the protection of your data. Your privacy and security are our top priority.</p>

    <h4>6. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: support@abc-retail.com.</p>
</div>

